Title: What I think about when I edit — Eva Parish
Description: I’m often asked to edit friends’ or coworkers’ writing, anything from emails to short stories to documentation. Recently, someone asked me  how  I edit. What am I looking for? How do I know what changes to make? That made me stop and think about what I’ve been doing semi-instinctually.

Title: Master Claims Transformation for Flexible ASP.NET Core Authorization
Description: Claims-based authorization mechanisms are central to modern authorization in ASP.NET Core. However, the access tokens issued by your Identity Provider (IDP) might not always perfectly align with your application's internal authorization needs. The solution? Claims transformation.
